{
  "stem": "25651.15",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Come and see me every day because I'll get you on to this transport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for a month I kept visiting Viktor at the office there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I lived with Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Novotny, and I waited for these bombers to come from England to bring the Czech Air Force to take the children from Theresienstadt to, to England.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it took a month-- from mid-July to mid-August.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We arrived in Windemere on the 15th of August 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next day.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a story-- amongst the stories that I gave you, there's a story about how the psychologist who was in charge of the whole operation in Windemere thought that me meeting my father would be a great shock to me.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't talk to me about psychologists and the logic of Freudian psychology.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's a whole-- it's quite an involved article about the Freudians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she thought that I would suffer some sort of trauma, so she had my father wait in a waiting room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was questioning me for half an hour, thinking that I could have some sort of delirium, you know, if I met my father.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after about half an hour's conversation I said her, for heaven's sakes, what are these questions for?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why are you asking me all this?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, get to the point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So finally she says, well, the point is your father is in the room next door.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was completely exasperated with this woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was this Alice Goldberger, who was such a good woman, you know, looked after the children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were-- there were little babies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Read the article.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's really quite--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
